{"tid":1851321,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港良心導演: 要提倡戲院黃圈, 就唔好只睇迪士尼/Marvel大片","createTime":"2020-01-30T03:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T10:42:12.000Z","uid":134071,"like":61,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4b9a8016bcccd324794659ab873d18ac1203e1","tid":1851321,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:46:59.000Z","msg":"某位導演, 拍左香港回歸以來最有良心既電影. &nbsp;(而且, 雖然佢拍左香港回歸以來最有良心既電影, 但好多自稱&quot;良心觀眾&quot;都係睇老翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n佢最近講得無錯: &nbsp;要提倡戲院黃圈, 就唔好只睇美國大片, 唔好只睇迪士尼/Marvel. <br />\n見到較可觀既本土電影/黃電影, 請盡量合法地支持. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想起黎, 自己無大力宣傳&quot;香港獨立電影節&quot;, 覺得好慚愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677880b5e4705bbf0a13bc7f53305447cb730bc4","tid":1851321,"uid":134071,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:47:18.000Z","msg":"近年黎. 會當有黃戲出黎, 總有人彈出一堆理由話要杯葛<br />\n結果杯葛成功, 但蝕底既係電影界黃絲手足.  <br />\n<br />\n《樹大招風》係香港上映時, 都有唔少網民話杯葛.  原因? 因為《樹大招風》有陳小春演出.<br />\n《十年》《樹大招風》導演歐文傑拍左套《非同凡響》, 批評香港教育制度. 但果時又有堆網友話女主角余香凝拜金, 叫人杯葛.<br />\n《G殺》係杜汶澤主演, 屌黑警.  上映時又有人話係小眾悶片, 無娛樂性, 唔撐場<br />\n<br />\n(結果而家, 反而多左好多人大讚《樹大招風》, 《非同凡響》, 《G殺》.  但電影基本上係以票房定命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"c2c260cf9336cb81963519f05cd65daf2f6ea4d9","tid":1851321,"uid":249263,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:48:42.000Z","msg":"求求大家<br />\n明白肺炎好恐怖<br />\n貨源都好緊張<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好放棄國際戰線<br />\n好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></span><br />\n全部英美議員講野唔過千<br />\n<br />\n已經連續三日都係咁<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=dd9aa707\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"d8278fc1950658c40dcd63e45ba64988bc621240","tid":1851321,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575bdb1a3c0ed9e40eed922d8656ec36f74d2500","tid":1851321,"uid":226155,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:53:25.000Z","msg":"根本唔好睇共迪"},{"pid":"92a88df119fcce89f3e162ccb73f6e26fe4cac1b","tid":1851321,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4cff3af462d5dab3f05b8e0ffed0e157abb994","tid":1851321,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"暫時電影界黃色經濟圈都幾失敗<br />\n係hkmovie造分造到最低既葉問4票房仲成功過葉問3<br />\n而想捧到上天既乜代宗師 雖然係咁比5星<br />\n但質素太低 票房好似過山車咁"},{"pid":"1f726ea4d9cca1ec44cbe3af184890d0f638adbf","tid":1851321,"uid":131122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"事實係香港有咁既觀眾就唔可能有好既電影<br />\n有點既市場，就有點既戲<br />\n想做好電影圏，香港需要文藝復興"},{"pid":"95f32a62eecf1ed72d89f3e370207f695d605dde","tid":1851321,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:04:09.000Z","msg":"上google play 買來睇 都好似百三四蚊"},{"pid":"670c0eb3a19dae5fe4e6000484cc8e9b10b73077","tid":1851321,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c4cff3af462d5dab3f05b8e0ffed0e157abb994","tid":1851321,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"暫時電影界黃色經濟圈都幾失敗<br />\n係hkmovie造分造到最低既葉問4票房仲成功過葉問3<br />\n而想捧到上天既乜代宗師 雖然係咁比5星<br />\n但質素太低 票房好似過山車咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:04:30.000Z","msg":"費事講黃子華<br />\n<br />\n以下三套片, 先係黃色電影圈既關鍵:<br />\n(叔叔/幻愛/金都)"},{"pid":"c47e2035a325bb612746a6420944d118876001ae","tid":1851321,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f726ea4d9cca1ec44cbe3af184890d0f638adbf","tid":1851321,"uid":131122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"事實係香港有咁既觀眾就唔可能有好既電影<br />\n有點既市場，就有點既戲<br />\n想做好電影圏，香港需要文藝復興"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"王晶係仆街,&nbsp; 拍好多垃圾片, 但佢鬧香港觀眾都可以睇下:<br />\n<br />\n王晶: 「𠵱家香港人，大部分都係沙漠英雄，又塵又冇水，仲要好 mean咁去睇笑片。你咁 mean，為數又少，我做咩要 serve你班咁認真嘅人，唔去 serve上邊十三億人啫？就算睇戲嗰班得五千萬人，都已經養得起成個電影業喇！<br />\n<br />\n唔係香港人唔算得啲咩，係做生意之嘛，邊個畀多啲錢咪邊個為主囉，我哋以前啲戲都係拍畀台灣人睇之嘛！全世界啲生意都唔係專為香港人而設，所有企業唯一係得 TVB一心一意拍嘢畀香港人睇。要鬧，你班友最唔應該鬧 TVB！你叻喇、巴閉喇，咪又係睇《來自星星的你》、《繼承者們》，咪一樣 foolish？有幾叻啫？咪又係因為靚仔？分別在於佢哋用多多錢、多多技術、同班好靚嘅仔去拍個 foolish story之嘛！ TVB對白三十年不變，係因為黎耀祥同麥長青講啫，換著張智霖講，你咪又係話好！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5014301&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5014301%26page%3D1&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=c793b042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5014301&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"758480b156846dc47acc09cf14994cabd5b16bc6","tid":1851321,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2685b057ee3c5c481a19d513b20fe19b20fb8186","tid":1851321,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"758480b156846dc47acc09cf14994cabd5b16bc6","tid":1851321,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,